data.description: NEW ROOF installed October 2023! Located in Downtown Bushnell this 3 bedroom/2 bathroom home, originally built in 1937, has been updated and renewed yet maintains its extraordinary charm and class. This 1,784 sqft home sits on a 1/4 acre corner lot inside the City limits of Bushnell yet offers plenty of privacy with a fenced in back yard featuring a 24 ft round above ground pool with a covered patio. Inside, the original hardwood floors have been beautifully restored with tile placed in the kitchen. The faux brick wall in the kitchen is a gorgeous site but there are plenty of other features to boast about - tons of kitchen cabinet space, large 18x14 family/bonus room that leads to the 2-car garage, living/dining combo with step down access to the family room and a covered front porch.  Conveniently close to major highways (I75, Florida's Turnpike, US 301, SR 471, SR 50) and centrally located for quick access and commute to Ocala, Tampa, Orlando and The Villages. Call today for a private showing.
